---
import { siteConfig } from "../../config/site"
---

<section class="py-20 bg-neutral-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
        <img
          src="/img/profile.jpg"
          alt="Profile"
          class="rounded-full w-64 h-64 object-cover mx-auto shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Me</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 mb-6">
          Hi, I am a backend engineer specializing in web application
          development. I have experience developing and operating business
          systems using Java (SpringBoot) and AWS. Recently, I have been working
          on personal web services. I strive to write "clear and functional
          code" and continue learning and improving every day. Additionally, I
          share what I learn through personal projects and technical blogs.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            href={siteConfig.links.github}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-neutral-900 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors"
          >
            GitHub Profile
          </a>
          <a
            href={siteConfig.links.x}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-neutral-900 border border-neutral-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-100 transition-colors"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
